    /* ‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏Ç‡∏ô‡∏≤‡∏î Input ‡∏™‡∏µ‡πÉ‡∏ô‡∏°‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏ñ‡∏∑‡∏≠ */
    .color-picker-container { width: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 5px; }
